      "notes": "CONFIRMED: exact birth/death dates per WikiTree (Langham-444). Parents: Clarence E. White (2 Oct 1893 - 4 Sep 1949, Cape Horn, Skamania, WA) and Elsie M. Hill (27 May 1902 - 1 Apr 1999, Satsop, Grays Harbor, WA). Married Edgar Donald Langham. Three daughters: Carolyn Myers, Marilyn Kenyon, Joanne Sorenson. Preceded in death by husband Edgar (2010) and son Donald Arthur Langham (2011). Five grandchildren, five great-grandchildren."
    },
