      "birthDate": "1924-08-25",
      "deathDate": "2012-09-15",
      "birthPlace": "Huntington, Cabell County, West Virginia",
      "deathPlace": "Longview, Washington",
      "notes": "CONFIRMED: exact birth/death dates per WikiTree (Langham-444). Born Aug. 25, 1924 in Huntington, WV; died Sept. 15, 2012 in Longview, WA; buried Satsop Cemetery. Navy veteran served in South Pacific during WWII. Worked for Northern Pacific Railroad and retired from Burlington Northern Railroad. Preceded in death by wife Jacqueline Avis (White) Langham (2010) and son Donald Arthur Langham (2011). Survived by three daughters including Joanne and Olaf Sorenson, five grandchildren, and five great-grandchildren."
    },
